<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
	
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>

		
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=531996">Shadow Heaven</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Hardam's Deliveries</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Hardam's Deliveries</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=541526"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Mrreowl - Ant Bayle</a> | 
		                        1/3/2002 7:22:03 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Hardam sells armour near the upper entrance to the Stout Quarter. Take the stairs (on the left wall in the cavern), follow them through and he is just inside the first building on your left.<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'Hail, Hardam Stonegrinder'<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'In need of some ores or other mining supplies? Well step right up, I got everything ye could possibly need! Also I'll have more supplies coming in as soon as I can get some dern time to deliver my [payment] to the commissioner. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what payment?'<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'Well ya see mate I have a representative of me great mining business here that is currently in the bazaar, however I got some new things I need him to sell but I can't leave me shop! I just need to get these new [items] to him so that he can sell them. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what items?'<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'Well da usual items ya know. I gets a lot of different goods in here every day and it is important that I move em out as fast as possible when they worth more ya knows? If ye lewkin for a [task] I've heard about ye around town and ye seem to be a trustworthy person. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what task?'<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'I'm simply lookin for someone to take me box of [goods] here to my friend in the bazaar, his name is Faeroi and he will know what to do with them. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'i will take the goods'<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'I thank ya for your willingness to help, Mrreowl. Here is the box of the different things I need taken to Faeroi. When I spoke to him before he left for the bazaar this morning he told me that the helm that I had been having customized was ready. I have enclosed a note for him to give that to you to return to me. I look forward to seeing you soon. <BR>
<BR>
Receive: a box of goodies for Faeori.<BR>
<BR>
Faeroi is in The Bazaar at -600 150. turn in the box to him:<BR>
<BR>
Faeroi says 'Ah Hardam sent you eh. Fair enough then, please let him know I will get to selling these goods as soon as possible and please let him know that the helm will be done soon. All I need is a certain [piece]. <BR>
<BR>
Your faction standing with House of Stout got better.<BR>
Your faction standing with Traders of the Haven got better.<BR>
You gain experience!!<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what piece?'<BR>
<BR>
Faeroi says 'Im waiting to have a rhino beetle horn delivered to me to finish off Hardams helm. I do not want to present it to him with one horn you know. If you wanted to be a big help any rhino beetles horn would do fine. Bring one to me and I can then finish Hardams helm and send it back to his shop in your hands. <BR>
<BR>
I happened to have a Rhino Beetle Horn (LORE) in the bank from my hunting in Shadeweaver's Thicket (he says any horn will do, so perhaps the ivory horns, cracked, flawless etc will also suffice.) I turned that in...<BR>
<BR>
Faeroi says 'Its good to see you again so soon Mrreowl. I knew that you would be able to assist me in this task. As I said , here is Hardams finished helm. Please return it to him for me as I cannot leave my booth here. <BR>
<BR>
Your faction standing with House of Stout got better.<BR>
Your faction standing with Traders of the Haven got better.<BR>
You gain experience!!<BR>
<BR>
Receive a helm to return to Hardam (not equippable).<BR>
<BR>
Return to Hardam and hand in the helm:<BR>
<BR>
Hardam Stonegrinder says 'Ah what a pleasant surprise indeed it seems my Helm is done! Many thanks for all your help once again Mrreowl. And safe travels to you. <BR>
<BR>
Your faction standing with House of Stout got better.<BR>
Your faction standing with Traders of the Haven got better.<BR>
You gain experience!!<BR>

			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
